    dr, mt, rd, se, dc, oa, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, ev, 